Description: A data set that is produced as the output of a normalization data transformation.
A file of data containing multiple values for multiple samples.
A data file produced by an instrument, or one with very little subsequent processing.

A file of clinical, technical, or other parameters that describe a dataset.
An activity that stands as an equivalent of something or results in an equivalent; typical of, or the same as, others in a larger group of people or things.
